text: 25 Churchill Place is a skyscraper in the eastern part of the London financial district Canary Wharf. Potential tenants included Aon, Deutsche Bank and News Corp. == Information == It is 118 metres (387 ft) and it opened in 2014, the same year when construction was completed after two years of construction. ===Tenants=== *Ernst & Young (Floors 14 to 21) *Wework (Floors 1 to 11 and 13) Category:Skyscrapers in the United Kingdom Category:Buildings and structures in the London Borough of Tower Hamlets
title: 25 Churchill Place
